## Coaching programmes: unlocking the full potential of managers and teams \*\*Today more than ever,

circumstances make it necessary to be able to provide a collaborator – at any hierarchical level – or a team, with a "safe space" that is both non-judgemental and enabling, to step back, explore options, refine their ability to adjust their relational skills, maintain their resilience…\*_ **In short, to be more effective, in a healthy and "sustainable" way!**

## But what is coaching in
practice? When we support you, we are particularly attentive to - The diagnostic phase, during which we will help you bring out your own needs and objectives - Putting your own responsibility at the heart of your work, which is expressed in the freedom of your choices - Respecting your pace and your ecosystem - The quality of the alliance between us: a relationship of trust and a relational contract that covers both the purposes of our work together, but also the modalities of our common work and the health of our relationship - The ethics and confidentiality of our exchanges _ \* \* ## INDIVIDUAL COACHING _**Having a dedicated "space-time" to develop a "win-win" relationship with your organization, by accessing the keys to flourishing, unleashing your potential and increasing collective performance**_

#### Executive coaching To get out of isolation, step back, work on
specific issues and posture challenges, in a relationship that is external and "neutral", capable of benevolent but unsparing confrontation. _Customised journey of 6 to 10 individual sessions_ #### Manager coaching To help you assume this unique position in the organization, and enable you to deploy yourself there, for the benefit of your teams. When a problem is identified by the manager or their hierarchy, or in support of key moments in their evolution: taking up a position, leadership posture to assume, transition… _Customised journey of 6 to 10 individual sessions, for a specific issue or professional guidance_ _Support over 3 months adapted to the company for a new role_ ## TEAM COACHING _**Creating the conditions to develop team cohesion and collective effectiveness.**_ _**Reducing friction by unblocking rigid attitudes, sources of misunderstanding, wasted energy and collective ineffectiveness**_

#### Facilitation and animation of team time-outs Such as CoDir
meetings, visioning work, seminars and team-building…

#### Leadership development through
**Intent-Based Leadership** deployment Through collective workshops, shadowing (on-site follow-up with debriefing), …

#### Improvement of relational processes By optimising inter-individual
relationships and resolving conflict or rigidity within a team _Customised support from half a day_

